properties.Name: GenbankFormatSequenceValueType
properties.Description:
A potential value for a position in the GenBank file sequence.

Ex:
-  ORIGIN (The start of the sequence is marked by a line starting with "SQ" )
- // ( the end of the sequence is marked by two slashes)
- A
- C  
- T
- G
